OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright with
OL,6,Fa scattering of showers this evening,
OL,7,Fthen mainly dry across Shetland
OL,8,Fovernight. Thickening cloud and patchy
OL,9,Frain pushing into Orkney later in the
OL,10,Fnight. Winds mostly light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FIt will be mostly cloudy with
OL,13,Frain or showers, but drier and
OL,14,Fbrighter across Shetland during the
OL,15,Fmorning. Winds light or moderate from
OL,16,Fthe east or southeast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
