OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry and bright on Monday with sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Windy with rain giving way to
OL,8,Fshowers on Tuesday. Occasional showers
OL,9,Fon Wednesday with easing winds.
